 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CBC6B1><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzatrizspiritscale.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zatriz Spiritscale</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Pippified Lizard King</span><br> <font color=#8E9173>(8/7/01 11:12:58 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My experience in PoG...</span><hr size=1> I hear that very few of the monsters in PoG see Invis.  The PoGs (Protectors of Growth) and some of the named Treants are about the only things that see invis. <p><hr>
